NAME
    Stump - Larry Wall's Slideshow Software

SYNOPSIS
        > stump init
        > edit stump.input
        > stump make
        > stump speech

DESCRIPTION
    Stump is Larry Wall's slideshow presentation hacks, packaged up for
    CPAN.

    Stump takes a simple input format and some pictures and whatnot, and
    compiles them into a OpenDocument (.odp) file that you view with your
    favorite slideshow software.

AUTHOR
